---
title: "auctionCallback (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_paused: require whenNotPaused
    q_check_paused --> q_check_caller: not paused
    q_check_caller --> q_revert_forbidden: msg.sender != s_auction OR from != address(this)
    q_revert_forbidden --> [*]: revert AccessForbidden
    q_check_caller --> q_decode: authorized caller
    q_decode --> q_multicall: calls = decode(data)
    q_multicall --> q_approve: _multiCall(calls)
    q_approve --> [*]: forceApprove(msg.sender, amountOut)

    note right of q_multicall
        INV-001: Only the configured auction contract can invoke callback
        INV-002: from must be this contract (self-initiated bid only)
        INV-003: Arbitrary calls executed via _multiCall to source settlement asset
        INV-004: Approval granted to auction contract for exact amountOut after solution execution
    end note
